\begin_layout Subsection
Markov Processes
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A Markov process(MP) is a stochastic process, which has a 
\emph on
continuous
\emph default
 parameter space T, discrete sample space 
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega$
\end_inset

 and the 
\emph on
Markov property
\emph default
 (refer equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
