\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
P(\mbox{arrival in }(t,t+h)) & = & 1-e^{-\lambda h}\\
 & = & \lambda h+o(h)
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
From the above result we get the instantaneous transition rates which can
 be then used to find the SSPD for the process.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
q_{ij} & = & \begin{cases}
